data.description: Nestled in the serene rural community of Ridge Harbor, this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is brimming with charm and character. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the spacious open floor plan, enhanced by vaulted ceilings and large windows that flood the space with natural light. The living room seamlessly flows into the dining area, creating the perfect space for both entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, and a convenient breakfast nook overlooking the patio. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or enjoying your morning coffee, this kitchen is sure to impress. Retreat to the master bedroom, where sliding glass doors lead out to the patio, offering a peaceful retreat to unwind after a long day. The ensuite bathroom boasts dual sinks and a luxurious walk-in shower, providing the ultimate in relaxation. With a new A/C unit installed in 2022, a water heater from 2021, and a new roof as recent as 2023, you can rest assured that your comfort is well taken care of. The addition of a security system not only enhances safety but also lowers the cost of homeowner's insurance. Outside, the screened-in back patio where new ceiling fans provide is the perfect spot to enjoy your morning cup of coffee while taking in the serene views of horses grazing in the backyard and the adjacent bamboo farm. And let's not forget about the delightful extras: a water filtration system under the kitchen sink, a water softening system, and new hot and cold water connections for the washer and dryer. Speaking of which, the washer and dryer are included with the home! But the perks don't stop there. The option to purchase the adjacent lot is also available, (listed separately on MLS with the reference number [MLS Number]), with this option you'll have plenty of space to expand and create your own private paradise. Close to botanical gardens, rum distillery, downtown PG, fisherman’s village, nature center, iguana land, military museum, gilchrist and laishley park, this home offers endless opportunities for exploration and leisure. Additionally, residents have the option to pay dues for access to the private boat ramp, adding convenience for water enthusiasts. Furthermore, the community hosts exciting events such as food truck Fridays, weekly bingo, and extravagant Halloween celebrations where almost every house participates. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a piece of rural paradise. Schedule a viewing today and experience all that this wonderful home has to offer!
